    • state

      private final javafx.beans.property.ObjectProperty<GrowthStage> state
      The growth stage of the plant.

    • seedQuality

      private float seedQuality
      The Seed quality. Not used in game.

    • waterNeeded

      private float waterNeeded
      The Water needed. The amount of water left until the plant is ripe.

    • waterDepletionRate

      private float waterDepletionRate
      The Water depletion rate. The rate at which the plant consumes water.

    • maxWater

      private float maxWater
      The Max water. The starting point of how much water the plant needed.

    • nutritionNeeded

      private float nutritionNeeded
      The Nutrition needed. The amount of nutrition left until the plant is ripe.

    • nutritionDepletionRate

      private float nutritionDepletionRate
      The Nutrition depletion rate. The rate at which the plant consumes nutrition.

    • maxNutrition

      private float maxNutrition
      The Max nutrition. The starting point of how much nutrition the plant needed.

    • growthTime

      private int growthTime
      The Growth time. The minimum time that the plant needs to grow, only relevant if the plant grows too quickly due to a too high depletion rate.

    • maxTimeWithoutWater

      private int maxTimeWithoutWater
      The Max time without water. The amount of update ticks a plant can go without withering and becoming GrowthStage.DEAD.

    • ticksNotWatered

      private int ticksNotWatered
      The Ticks not watered. Amount of update ticks the plant has gone without the waterNeeded attribute being changed.

    • growTicks

      private int growTicks
      The Grow ticks. Total amount of update ticks.
